```plantuml
@startuml onprem_foundry

[Furnace] as furnace
[Package Management] as pkgmgmt
[Metrics and Health Checks] as metrics
[Object Storage] as storage
[Builder Interface] as builder
[gRPC Server] as grpc
[Configuration] as config
[CLI] as cli

furnace --> pkgmgmt : manages packages
furnace --> metrics : exposes
furnace --> storage : uploads packages
furnace --> builder : uses
furnace --> grpc : exposes API

cli --> config : reads
config --> furnace : configures

grpc <-- [Client] : requests builds

builder <|-- [MakepkgBuilder]
builder <|-- [NoOpBuilder]

[BuilderWithMetrics] .> builder : decorates

@enduml
```